reviewText: My Grandson is addicted lol much rather have him watch these then some of the cartoons on tv
Bought as a Christmas present and they loved it.
My four year old Jacob and 11 year Wyatt, loved it. Anything dealing with The Big Green Tractors makes them smile. Good Job John Deere:)
These dvd's are something my 5 year old grandson has watched for years.  Even Grandma thinks they're interesting.  They're truly geared for kids and I purchased another set for my 3 yr old grandson
